## 4. Screens & Navigation

### 4.1 Screen map

```
Login
  └── Home (Rack grid)
        └── Rack detail
              └── Row detail
                    └── Bin detail
                          └── Item detail
```

Breadcrumb navigation on every inner screen allows jumping back to any ancestor level.

### 4.2 Login screen

- Branding: **YesStore**
- Fields: User ID, Password
- Actions: Sign in, Register (toggle)
- User ID input: letters, numbers, dots, dashes only; auto-lowercased

### 4.3 Home — Rack grid

- Grid of all **24 valid rack letters**
- Each card shows:
  - Rack letter (large), or thumbnail of first rack photo if any exist
  - Photo count
- Tap a rack → Rack detail

### 4.4 Rack detail

- Header: rack letter, subtitle “Rows 1–7”
- **Rack photos** section (upload / view / delete)
- Grid of **rows 1–7** (same card pattern: number or thumbnail + photo count)
- Tap a row → Row detail

### 4.5 Row detail

- Header: `Rack X · Row N`, subtitle “Bins 1–9”
- **Row photos** section
- Grid of **bins 1–9**
- Tap a bin → Bin detail

### 4.6 Bin detail

- Header: full location `Rack X · Row N · Bin N`
- **Bin photos** section
- **Items** section:
  - Form to add item: name, notes, **required photos** (see §5.2)
  - List of existing items with thumbnails, photo count, delete action
  - Items without photos are highlighted with a warning
- Tap an item → Item detail

### 4.7 Item detail

- Header: item name, notes (if any), location tag
- **Item photos** section (required — at least one photo expected per item)

