## 6. Data Entities (Logical Model)

For integration into the master project’s database/API:

### Rack

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `id` | string | Single letter (valid rack letter) |
| `photos` | Photo[] | Optional |
| `createdAt` | datetime | |
| `updatedAt` | datetime | |

### Row

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `id` | string | Row number as string (`"1"` … `"7"`) |
| `number` | integer | 1–7 |
| `rackId` | string | Parent rack |
| `photos` | Photo[] | Optional |
| `createdAt` | datetime | |
| `updatedAt` | datetime | |

### Bin

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `id` | string | Bin number as string (`"1"` … `"9"`) |
| `number` | integer | 1–9 |
| `rackId` | string | Parent rack |
| `rowId` | string | Parent row |
| `photos` | Photo[] | Optional |
| `createdAt` | datetime | |
| `updatedAt` | datetime | |

### Item

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `id` | string | Unique identifier |
| `name` | string | Required |
| `notes` | string | Optional |
| `rackId`, `rowId`, `binId` | string | Parent location |
| `photos` | Photo[] | **Required (min 1)** |
| `createdAt` | datetime | |
| `updatedAt` | datetime | |

### Photo

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `id` | string | Unique identifier |
| `url` | string | Public/download URL for display |
| `fileName` | string | Original file name |
| `uploadedAt` | datetime | |

**Lazy creation:** Rack, row, and bin records are created on first visit or first photo upload — the UI always shows the full grid of valid racks/rows/bins even if no data exists yet.

