## 7. UI / UX Characteristics

| Topic | Detail |
|-------|--------|
| **Theme** | Dark industrial UI; blue accent |
| **Layout** | Single-column, max-width content; touch-friendly buttons (min ~40px) |
| **Grids** | Responsive auto-fill grids for racks, rows, bins |
